snippet.title: [Vinesauce] Joel - Todd Howard Visual Novel
snippet.description:
Joel played my Todd Howard game in September, but he never uploaded it to youtube so I downloaded it when i had the chance and since the VOD's expired i figured i'd upload it.

Joel - https://www.twitch.tv/vargskelethor/

Game - https://easterlil.itch.io/todd-howard-dating-sim

I was gonna trim the video but it would take to long to render and my computers bad.
